      "text": "……そうね。あの子達は、長瀬麻奈の心や魂に触れ\nそれを自らのものとして受け継いでいるのだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes. Those kids have touched Nagase Mana's heart and soul\nand inherited them as their own…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.77868616656076,
      "endTime": 306.63979761679997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
